1. *Gubitnik* je odustao od trke. (The *loser* gave up on the race.)
2. *Gubitnik* je bio razočaran svojim rezultatom. (The *loser* was disappointed with his result.)
3. On je osuđen na *gubitak*. (He is doomed to *loss*.)
4. Njegov posao je bio *gubitnički* od samog početka. (His business was *losing* from the start.)
5. Nije fer smatrati ga *gubitnikom* samo zato što nije pobijedio. (It's not fair to label him a *loser* just because he didn't win.)
6. *Gubitnički* mentalitet neće doneti uspeh. (*Loser* mentality won't bring success.)
7. U ovoj igri, svi su pobednici osim *gubitnika*. (In this game, everyone is a winner except the *loser*.)
8. Nema smisla žaliti za *gubitkom*, moramo se usredsrediti na budućnost. (There's no point in lamenting over *loss*, we need to focus on the future.)
9. Ne želim da budem *gubitnik* u ovom sporu. (I don't want to be the *loser* in this dispute.)
10. On nije mogao da prihvati *poraz* i postao je *gubitnički* u svojim postupcima. (He couldn't accept *defeat* and became *loser-like* in his actions.)